  Home  Analyst Ratings  Analyst Downgrades – Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX) Stock Gets Downgraded...     Analyst Ratings  Analyst Downgrades – Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX) Stock Gets Downgraded By Macquarie from Neutral to Underperform  ByME Staff -July 27, 2017 0  Share on Facebook
Tweet on Twitter


 Analyst Ratings For Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX)
Today, Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX) stock was downgraded by Macquarie from Neutral to Underperform.
There are 1 sell rating, 2 hold ratings, 9 buy ratings on the stock.
The current consensus rating on Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX) is Buy (Score: 2.67) with a consensus target price of $66.50 per share, a potential 12.27% upside.
Some recent analyst ratings include

7/27/2017-Macquarie was Downgraded by analysts at Macquarie from a “Neutral ” rating to a ” Underperform” rating.
7/21/2017-William Blair initiated coverage with a Outperform rating.
7/19/2017-FBR & Co Reiterated Rating of Buy.
7/14/2017-Stifel Nicolaus Reiterated Rating of Buy.
6/20/2017-Wedbush Reiterated Rating of Outperform.
5/1/2017-Goldman Sachs Group, Inc. (The) Reiterated Rating of Neutral.
4/29/2017-B. Riley Reiterated Rating of Buy.

Dividend information for Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX)
Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX) pays an annual dividend of Community Ranking:  with a yield of 4.32% and an average dividend growth of 9.40% based on a 3 Year Average.
Dividend History for Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New (NYSE:SIX)

On 5/4/2017 Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New announced a quarterly dividend of $0.64 4.03% with an ex dividend date of 5/23/2017 which will be payable on 6/12/2017.
On 2/9/2017 Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New announced a quarterly dividend of $0.64 4.23% with an ex dividend date of 2/27/2017 which will be payable on 3/13/2017.
On 11/9/2016 Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New announced a quarterly dividend of $0.64 4.5% with an ex dividend date of 11/29/2016 which will be payable on 12/12/2016.
On 8/25/2016 Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New announced a quarterly dividend of $0.58 4.65% with an ex dividend date of 8/30/2016 which will be payable on 9/12/2016.
On 5/5/2016 Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New announced a quarterly dividend of $0.58 4% with an ex dividend date of 5/24/2016 which will be payable on 6/13/2016.
On 2/4/2016 Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New announced a quarterly dividend of $0.58 4.82% with an ex dividend date of 2/11/2016 which will be payable on 3/7/2016.
On 11/4/2015 Six Flags Entertainment Corporation New announced a quarterly dividend of $0.58 4.47% with an ex dividend date of 11/30/2015 which will be payable on 12/14/2015.

