Higher Than AverageThe principal Product or Service Code (PSC) of Six Flags Entertainment Corp is Lease/Rental of Miscellaneous Buildings (X1JZ) as measured by the total amount obligated in contract awards to the vendor since FY2007.In its latest full year of contract work (FY2012), Six Flags Entertainment Corp was obligated a total of $5,000, an amount that was far higher than the average vendor from Missouri specializing in Lease/Rental of Miscellaneous Buildings and 34% lower than all vendors in the U.S. classified by this PSC.
